OL,3,C#710 million hospital given planning
OL,4,Cpermission
OL,6,FWork on Jersey's new #710 million
OL,7,Facute hospital at Overdale could begin
OL,8,Flater this year after the Planning
OL,9,FCommittee unanimously signed off on
OL,10,Fthe plans.
OL,12,FThere was relief in the room when the
OL,13,Fdecision was announced, potentially
OL,14,Fdrawing a line under many years of
OL,15,Fdiscussions and delays.
OL,17,FConcerns continued to be raised about
OL,18,Fparking with only 343 spaces planned
OL,19,Fbut this was not judged to be enough
OL,20,Fto delay the proposals.
