OL,6,FThe designs include more than 200
OL,7,Fovernight beds and modern versions of
OL,8,Fthe General Hospital's current
OL,9,Ffacilities with an estimated
OL,10,Fcompletion year of 2028.
OL,12,FIf spades are put in the ground before
OL,13,Fthe next election in 2026, the
OL,14,Fincoming States will not be able to
OL,15,Foverrule or U-turn the plans in place.
OL,17,FThe New Healthcare Facilities
OL,18,FProgramme aims to build across
OL,19,Fmultiple locations, including an acute
OL,20,Ffacility at Overdale in St Helier and
OL,21,Fa health village in St Saviour.
