OL,6,FThe Government hopes this choice will
OL,7,Ffinally conclude the decade-long
OL,8,Fpursuit of a new hospital.
OL,10,FLast year, it was reported that over
OL,11,F#130 million had been spent on various
OL,12,Fprojects under different
OL,13,Fadministrations.
OL,15,FThis included plans for an #800
OL,16,Fmillion health campus from the
OL,17,Fprevious "Our Hospital" scheme, which
OL,18,Fwas managed by Deputy Lyndon Farnham
OL,19,Fduring his time in John Le Fondre's
OL,20,Fgovernment.
