OL,6,FThese designs were abandoned in 2022
OL,7,Ffollowing a review conducted by Deputy
OL,8,FTom Binet, who was Infrastructure
OL,9,FMinister at the time.
OL,11,FDeputy Binet, now Jersey's Health
OL,12,FMinister, says: "The approval marks a
OL,13,Fmajor milestone in delivering the
OL,14,Fmodern, high-quality healthcare
OL,15,Ffacilities our island urgently needs.
