OL,6,F"It's a weight off everyone's
OL,7,Fshoulders but bear in mind it's not
OL,8,Fthe end of the saga, it's the
OL,9,Fbeginning of the end and let's hope it
OL,10,Fis as it has been going on for far too
OL,11,Flong.
OL,13,F"At the moment I think healthcare is
OL,14,Fpretty comprised and this cannot
OL,15,Fhappen quickly enough."
OL,17,FChief Minister Lyndon Farnham adds:
OL,18,F"It's significant but we aren't to
OL,19,Fdwell or celebrate the planning
OL,20,Fpermission, we just have to get on and
OL,21,Fbuild it."
